-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                 |                      |1       |652         |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE              |                      |1       |651         |
|2 |  └─TEMP TABLE TRANSFORMATION      |                      |1       |651         |
